"cyfeiriad:"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/index.html:5
msgid "My next election"
msgstr "Fy etholiad nesaf"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/index.html:17
msgid ""
"Enter your postcode to find out about voting in your next election. We'll"
" tell you who's standing, where your polling station is, and who to "
"contact if you need help."
msgstr ""
"Nodwch eich cod post i gael gwybodaeth am bleidleisio yn eich etholiad "
"nesaf. Fe wnawn ni ddweud wrthych pwy sy'n sefyll, lle mae eich gorsaf "
"bleidleisio, a phwy i cyswllt os oes angen help arnoch."

#: postcode_lookup/templates/index.html:25
msgid "Enter your postcode"
msgstr "Nodwch god post dilys"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/index.html:41
msgid "For example SW1A 2AA"
msgstr "Er enghraifft SW1A 2AA"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/index.html:99
msgid "What this tool can tell you"
msgstr "Beth all yr offeryn hwn ddweud wrthych"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/index.html:104
msgid "Which elections are happening in my area?"
msgstr "Pa etholiadau sy'n digwydd yn fy ardal?"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/index.html:105
#, 
msgid ""
"When you enter your postcode, you’ll find out which elections are coming "
"up in your area. This includes UK Parliamentary general elections, "
"Scottish Parliament elections, Senedd elections, local elections, mayoral"
" elections, Police and Crime Commissioner elections and by-elections."
msgstr ""
"Pan fyddwch chi’n mewnbynnu eich cod post, byddwch chi’n darganfod pa "
"etholiadau a fydd yn digwydd yn eich ardal. Mae hyn yn cynnwys etholiadau"
" cyffredinol Senedd y DU, etholiadau Senedd Cymru, etholiadau Senedd yr "
"Alban, etholiadau lleol, etholiadau maerol, etholiadau ac is-etholiadau "
"Comisiynwyr yr Heddlu a Throseddu."

#: postcode_lookup/templates/index.html:111
msgid "Where is my polling station?"
msgstr "Ble fy ngorsaf bleidleisio?"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/index.html:112
#, 
msgid ""
"Your polling station might not be the same for every election. Check "
"which polling station you need to go to for the next election in your "
"area."
msgstr ""
"Efallai na fydd eich gorsaf bleidleisio’r un peth ar gyfer pob etholiad. "
"Gwiriwch pa orsaf bleidleisio bydd angen i chi fynd iddi ar gyfer yr "
"etholiad nesaf yn eich ardal."

#: postcode_lookup/templates/index.html:116
msgid "What do I need to take with me when I vote?"
msgstr "Beth sydd angen i mi ei gymryd gyda mi pan fyddaf yn pleidleisio?"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/index.html:117
#, 
msgid ""
"Some elections might require you to take photo ID and some might not. "
"When you enter your postcode, you will find out if you need photo ID to "
"vote in the elections coming up in your area. You do not need to take "
"your poll card to vote."
msgstr ""
"Mae’n bosibl y bydd rhai etholiadau’n gofyn am ID ffotograffig, ac mae’n "
"bosibl na fydd eraill yn gofyn amdano. Pan fyddwch chi’n mewnbynnu eich "
"cod post, byddwch yn canfod a oes angen ID ffotograffig arnoch i "
"bleidleisio yn yr etholiadau a fydd yn digwydd yn eich ardal. Nid oes "
"angen i chi fynd â’ch cerdyn pleidleisio gyda chi i bleidleisio."

#: postcode_lookup/templates/index.html:122
msgid "Who can I vote for?"
msgstr "Pwy alla i bleidleisio ar gyfer?"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/index.html:123
#, 
msgid "Enter your postcode to find out who the candidates in your area are."
msgstr "Mewnbynnwch eich cod post i ganfod pwy yw’r ymgeiswyr yn eich ardal."

#: postcode_lookup/templates/old_result.html:21
#: postcode_lookup/templates/old_result.html:45
msgid "There is a recall petition in your area"
msgstr "Mae deiseb adalw yn eich ardal"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/results.html:25
msgid "On this page"
msgstr "Ar y dudalen hon"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/ballot_model.html:10
msgid "This ballot has been cancelled"
msgstr "Mae'r bleidlais hon wedi'i chanslo"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/ballot_model.html:16
msgid "This election takes place on"
msgstr "Bydd yr etholiad hwn yn cael ei gynnal ar"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/ballot_model.html:17
msgid "Find out more about voting in this election"
msgstr "Dysgwch ragor am bleidleisio yn yr etholiad hwn"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/ballot_model.html:44
#, python-format
msgid ""
"<p>Visit <a "
"href=&quot;https://whocanivotefor.co.uk/elections/%(postcode)s&quot; "
"target=&quot;_blank&quot; class=&quot;o-external-link&quot;>Who Can I "
"Vote For <span class=&quot;visually-hidden&quot;>(Opens in new "
"window)</span></a> to find out more about your candidates</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>Ewch <a "
"href=&quot;https://whocanivotefor.co.uk/elections/%(postcode)s&quot; "
"target=&quot;_blank&quot; class=&quot;o-external-link&quot;>Who Can I "
"Vote For <span class=&quot;visually-hidden&quot;>(Opens in new "
"window)</span></a> i ddysgu rhagor am eich ymgeiswyr</p>"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/ballots.html:10
msgid "parties and independent candidates"
msgstr "pleidiau ac ymgeiswyr annibynnol"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/ballots.html:12
msgid "candidates"
msgstr "ymgeiswyr"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/ballots.html:30
msgid "Find out more about the candidates in your area on WhoCanIVoteFor.co.uk"
msgstr "Dysgwch ragor am yr ymgeiswyr yn eich ardal ar WhoCanIVoteFor.co.uk"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/ballots.html:39
#, python-format
msgid ""
"<h3>%(ballot_title)s candidates</h3> <p>The list of candidates for this "
"election will be published after %(sopn_date)s.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<h3>%(ballot_title)s Ymgeiswyr</h3> <p>Cyhoeddir rhestr yr ymgeiswyr ar "
"gyfer yr etholiad hwn ar ôl %(sopn_date)s.</p>"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/cancellation_reasons.html:3
msgid "Postponed Election"
msgstr "Etholiad wedi'i ohirio"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/cancellation_reasons.html:5
#, python-format
msgid ""
"This election has been postponed due to the death of one of the "
"candidates. A new election will be held within 35 working days of the "
"initial election date (%(initial_poll_date)s)."
msgstr ""
"Mae'r etholiad hwn wedi'i ohirio oherwydd marwolaeth un o'r ymgeiswyr. "
"Bydd etholiad newydd yn cael ei gynnal o fewn 35 diwrnod gwaith o'r "
"dyddiad etholiad cychwynnol (%(initial_poll_date)s)."

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/cancellation_reasons.html:15
#, python-format
msgid ""
"No candidates stood for the available seats, so no election can be held. "
"The election will be rescheduled and held within 35 days of the original "
"polling day (%(initial_poll_date)s)."
msgstr ""
"Canslwyd yr etholiad hwn oherwydd na safodd unrhyw ymgeiswyr ar gyfer y "
"seddau sydd ar gael. Bydd yn cael ei aildrefnu a'i gynnal o fewn 35 "
"diwrnod gwaith o'r diwrnod pleidleisio cychwynnol "
"(%(initial_poll_date)s)."

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/cancellation_reasons.html:24
msgid "Uncontested Election"
msgstr "Etholiad heb gystadleuaeth"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/cancellation_reasons.html:27
msgid ""
"No election will be held because the number of candidates who stood was "
"equal to the number of available seats. The following candidates will "
"take up this position:"
msgstr ""
"Ni chynhelir etholiad oherwydd bod nifer yr ymgeiswyr a safodd yn hafal i"
" nifer y seddi sydd ar gael. Bydd yr ymgeiswyr canlynol yn cymryd y swydd"
" hon:"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/cancellation_reasons.html:42
#, python-format
msgid ""
"This election was postponed because the number of candidates who stood "
"was fewer than the number of available seats. The election will be "
"rescheduled and held within 35 days of the original polling day "
"(%(initial_poll_date)s)."
msgstr ""
"Fe ohiriwyd yr etholiad hwn gan fod nifer yr ymgeiswyr a safodd yn llai "
"na nifer y seddau sydd ar gael. Bydd yr etholiad yn cael ei aildrefnu a'i"
" gynnal o fewn 35 diwrnod o'r diwrnod pleidleisio gwreiddiol "
"(%(initial_poll_date)s)."

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/feedback_section.html:2
msgid "Feedback"
msgstr "Adborth"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/feedback_section.html:4
msgid ""
"Did you find what you were looking for? If not, <a "
"href=\"/node/24756\">let us know</a>"
msgstr ""
"A wnaethoch chi ddod o hyd i'r hyn roeddech yn chwilio amdano? Os na, <a "
"href=\"/node/24756\">rhowch wybod i ni</a>"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/html_meta.html:9
msgid ""
"Enter your postcode to find your electoral services team at your local "
"council. You need to send your postal and proxy vote application forms to"
" them."
msgstr ""
"Nodwch eich cod post i ddod o hyd i wybodaeth am eich tîm gwasanaeth "
"etholiadol yn eich cyngor lleol.Bydd angen i chi anfon eich ceisiadau "
"pleidlais bost neu bleidlais drwy ddirprwy i'ch gwasanaeth etholiadol "
"lleol."

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/html_meta.html:12
#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/html_meta.html:20
msgid "Elections in your area"
msgstr "Etholiadau yn eich ardal"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/html_meta.html:13
#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/html_meta.html:19
msgid ""
"Find upcoming elections in your area, your polling station, candidates, "
"and contact details for your local electoral services team"
msgstr ""
"Dewch o hyd i etholiadau sydd ar ddod yn eich ardal, eich gorsaf "
"bleidleisio, ymgeiswyr, a manylion cyswllt eich tîm gwasanaethau "
"etholiadol lleol"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/organisation_contact.html:4
msgid "Get help with electoral registration"
msgstr "Cael cymorth gyda chofrestru etholiadol"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/organisation_contact.html:7
msgid ""
"Send your postal and proxy vote applications to your local electoral "
"registration team. You can also contact them to find out if you’re on the"
" electoral register, and if you already have a postal or proxy vote."
msgstr ""
"Anfonwch eich ceisiadau pleidleisio post a dirprwy i'ch tîm cofrestru "
"etholiadol lleol. Gallwch hefyd gysylltu â hwy i ddarganfod a ydych chi "
"ar y gofrestr etholiadol, ac os oes gennych bleidlais post neu dirprwy "
"eisoes."

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/organisation_contact.html:17
msgid "Electoral Office for Northern Ireland"
msgstr "Swyddfa Etholiadol Gogledd Iwerddon"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/organisation_contact.html:19
msgid ""
"For questions about your poll card, polling place, or about returning "
"your postal voting ballot, contact the Electoral Office for Northern "
"Ireland."
msgstr ""
"Am gwestiynau am eich cerdyn pleidleisio, eich man pleidleisio, neu am "
"ddychwelyd eich papur pleidleisio post, cysylltwch â Swyddfa Etholiadol "
"Gogledd Iwerddon."

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/organisation_contact.html:27
msgid ""
"<p> For questions about your poll card, polling station, or about "
"returning your postal voting ballot, contact your returning officer. </p>"
msgstr ""
"<p> Os oes gennych gwestiynau am eich cerdyn pleidleisio, eich gorsaf "
"bleidleisio neu ynghylch eich pleidlais drwy’r post, cysylltwch â’ch "
"swyddog canlyniadau. </p>"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/organisation_contact.html:38
msgid ""
"<p> For questions about your poll card, polling station, or about "
"returning your postal voting ballot, contact your council. </p>"
msgstr ""
"<p> Am gwestiynau am eich cerdyn pleidleisio, eich gorsaf bleidleisio, "
"neu am ddychwelyd eich papur pleidleisio post, cysylltwch â'ch cyngor. "
"</p>"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/organisation_contact.html:46
msgid ""
"<p> Here are contact details for your usual election team. However, for "
"some elections, electoral boundaries mean that your neighbouring election"
" team may be responsible for the constituency you are in. Your usual "
"election team will be able to provide their contact details if this is "
"the case. </p>"
msgstr ""
"<p> Dyma fanylion cyswllt ar gyfer eich tîm etholiadau arferol. Fodd "
"bynnag, ar gyfer rhai etholiadau, bydd ffiniau etholiadol yn golygu "
"efallai mai eich tîm etholiadau cyfagos sy’n gyfrifol am yr etholaeth "
"rydych ynddi. Bydd eich tîm etholiadau arferol yn gallu rhoi eu manylion "
"cyswllt os dyma yw’r achos. </p>"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/organisation_contact.html:70
#, python-format
msgid "Phone: <span>%(number)s</span>"
msgstr "Ffôn: <span>%(number)s</span>"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/organisation_contact.html:80
#, python-format
msgid "Email: <span>%(email)s</span>"
msgstr "E-bost: <span>%(email)s</span>"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/organisation_contact.html:89
#, python-format
msgid "%(org_name)s website"
msgstr "Gwefan %(org_name)s"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/organisation_contact.html:92
msgid "Website"
msgstr "Gwefan"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/organisation_contact.html:94
msgid "(Opens in new window)"
msgstr "(Yn agor mewn ffenestr newydd)"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/polling_station.html:2
msgid "Your polling station"
msgstr "Eich gorsaf bleidleisio"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/polling_station.html:13
msgid ""
"You'll get a poll card in the post before the election. This will tell "
"you where to vote."
msgstr ""
"Fe gewch chi gerdyn pleidleisio yn y post cyn yr etholiad. Bydd hyn yn "
"dweud wrthych ble i bleidleisio."

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/polling_station.html:17
msgid ""
"If you haven’t received your polling card, <a href=\"#electoral-"
"services\">contact your returning officer</a>."
msgstr ""
"Os nad ydych wedi derbyn eich cerdyn pleidleisio, <a href=\"#electoral-"
"services\">cysylltwch â’ch swyddog canlyniadau</a>."

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/polling_station.html:19
msgid ""
"If you haven’t received your polling card, <a href=\"#electoral-"
"services\">contact your local council</a>."
msgstr ""
"Os nad ydych wedi derbyn eich cerdyn pleidleisio, <a href=\"#electoral-"
"services\">cysylltwch â’ch cyngor lleol</a>."

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/polling_station.html:23
msgid "Opening times"
msgstr "Oriau agor"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/postal_votes.html:3
#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/postal_votes.html:14
msgid "Apply for a postal vote"
msgstr "Gwneud cais i bleidleisio drwy'r post"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/postal_votes.html:5
msgid ""
"If you know that you won't be able to get to the polling station on "
"polling day, you can vote by post."
msgstr ""
"Os byddwch yn gwybod na fydd modd i chi gyrraedd eich gorsaf bleidleisio "
"ar y diwrnod pleidleisio, gallwch bleidleisio drwy'r post."

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/postal_votes.html:8
#, python-format
msgid "You have until %(date)s."
msgstr "Mae gennych hyd nes %(date)s"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/postal_votes.html:18
msgid "Read more about applying for a postal vote"
msgstr "Darllenwch fwy am wneud cais am bleidlais bost"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/postal_votes.html:23
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The deadline to apply for a postal vote for the elections taking place on"
" %(date)s was %(application_deadline)s. You can <a "
"href=\"https://www.gov.uk/apply-postal-vote\">apply for a postal vote</a>"
" in future elections."
msgstr ""
"%(application_deadline)s oedd y dyddiad cau i gofrestru am bleidlais bost"
" ar gyfer yr etholiadau ar %(date)s. Gallwch wneud cais am bleidlais bost"
" mewn etholiadau yn y dyfodol."

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/postal_votes.html:32
msgid "If you have a postal vote"
msgstr "Os oes gennych bleidlais bost"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/postal_votes.html:36
#, python-format
msgid ""
"<ul> <li>If you already have a postal vote or successfully apply by "
"%(date0)s, your pack will be sent from %(date1)s.</li> <li>If you apply "
"after %(date0)s up to 5pm on %(application_deadline)s, your pack will be "
"sent from %(date2)s.</li> </ul>"
msgstr ""
"<ul> <li>Os oes pleidlais bost gennych eisoes neu os ydych wedi gwneud "
"cais llwyddiannus erbyn %(date0)s, bydd eich pecyn yn cael ei anfon o "
"%(date1)s.</li> <li>Os byddwch yn gwneud cais ar ôl %(date0)s hyd at 5pm "
"ar %(application_deadline)s, bydd eich pecyn yn cael ei anfon o "
"%(date2)s.</li> </ul>"

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/postal_votes.html:50
msgid ""
"Your returning officer will send your postal voting pack after the "
"deadline to become a candidate has passed."
msgstr ""
"Bydd eich swyddog canlyniadau yn anfon eich pecyn pleidleisio drwy’r post"
" ar ôl i’r dyddiad cau ar gyfer dod yn ymgeisydd fynd heibio."

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/postal_votes.html:54
msgid ""
"Your local council will send your postal voting pack after the deadline "
"to become a candidate has passed."
msgstr ""
"Bydd eich cyngor lleol yn anfon eich pecyn pleidleisio drwy’r post ar ôl "
"i’r dyddiad cau ar gyfer dod yn ymgeisydd fynd heibio."

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/postal_votes.html:58
