msgstr "Mae hyn tua thair wythnos cyn y diwrnod pleidleisio."

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/postal_votes.html:66
#, python-format
msgid ""
"You can <a href=\"#electoral-services\">contact your local council</a> if"
" you have not received your postal voting pack. Replacement packs can "
"only be issued from %(replacement_pack_start_date)s until 5pm on "
"%(polling_day)s."
msgstr ""
"<a href=\"#electoral-services\">Gallwch gysylltu â’ch cyngor lleol</a> os"
" nad ydych wedi derbyn eich pecyn pleidleisio drwy’r post. Gellir dim ond"
" anfon pecynnau newydd o %(replacement_pack_start_date)s hyd nes 5pm ar "
"%(polling_day)s."

#: postcode_lookup/templates/includes/referendum.html:8
